snippet.title: sunteam
snippet.description: Retrogaming fan, mostly focused on NEC's PC Engine / TurboGrafx-16. Also a developer for new PC Engine, ZX Spectrum, Spectrum Next and MSX titles. I do not put adverts on any of my videos, so if there are any, they have been forced there by YouTube.
